trans-unit.source: You can set up bank accounts to keep track of transactions and import or export bank feeds, such as Yodlee.

seg-source.mrk: You can set up bank accounts to keep track of transactions and import or export bank feeds, such as Yodlee.

target.mrk: Můžete nastavit bankovní účty, abyste mohli sledovat transakce a importovat nebo exportovat bankovní zdroje, jako je například Yodlee.

trans-unit.source: Set Up the Bank Data Conversion Service

seg-source.mrk: Set Up the Bank Data Conversion Service

target.mrk: Nastavení služby převodu bankovních dat

trans-unit.source: A global provider of services to convert payment information to any data format that your bank requires is connected and ready to be enabled in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: A global provider of services to convert payment information to any data format that your bank requires is connected and ready to be enabled in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Globální poskytovatel služeb, který převádí informace o platbách do libovolného formátu dat, který banka vyžaduje, je připojen a připraven k zapnutí v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This is referred to in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] as the bank data conversion service.

seg-source.mrk: This is referred to in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] as the bank data conversion service.

target.mrk: Toto odkazuje na služba převodu bankovních dat v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: You can export payment lines from the **Payment Journal** page to a file or a data stream that you then upload to your bank for automatic processing so that you do not have to make electronic payments individually.

seg-source.mrk: You can export payment lines from the **Payment Journal** page to a file or a data stream that you then upload to your bank for automatic processing so that you do not have to make electronic payments individually.

target.mrk: Můžete exportovat platební řádky ze stránky **Deník plateb** do datového toku, který pak nahrajete do své banky pro automatické zpracování, takže nemusíte provádět elektronické platby individuálně.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Export Payments to a Bank File](payables-how-export-payments-bank-file.md).

seg-source.mrk: For more information, see [Export Payments to a Bank File](payables-how-export-payments-bank-file.md).

target.mrk: Další informace naleznete v části [Export plateb do Bankovních dokladů](payables-how-export-payments-bank-file.md).

trans-unit.source: You can import bank statement files into the **Payment Reconciliation Journal** page by using the bank data conversion service to convert a file that you receive from your bank to a data stream that [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] can import.

seg-source.mrk: You can import bank statement files into the **Payment Reconciliation Journal** page by using the bank data conversion service to convert a file that you receive from your bank to a data stream that [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] can import.

target.mrk: Soubory bankovních výpisů můžete importovat do **Deníku odsouhlasení plateb** pomocí služby převodu bankovních dat. Soubor, který obdržíte od své banky, do datového toku, který lze v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)]importovat.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Applying Payments Automatically and Reconciling Bank Accounts](receivables-apply-payments-auto-reconcile-bank-accounts.md).

seg-source.mrk: For more information, see [Applying Payments Automatically and Reconciling Bank Accounts](receivables-apply-payments-auto-reconcile-bank-accounts.md).

target.mrk: Další informace naleznete v části [Automatické vyrovnání plateb a odsouhlasení bankovních účtů](receivables-apply-payments-auto-reconcile-bank-accounts.md).

trans-unit.source: As an alternative to importing bank statements with the bank data conversion service, you can use the Envestnet Yodlee Bank Feeds service.

seg-source.mrk: As an alternative to importing bank statements with the bank data conversion service, you can use the Envestnet Yodlee Bank Feeds service.

target.mrk: Jako alternativu k importu bankovních výpisů pomocí služby převodu bankovních údajů můžete použít službu Envestnet Yodlee Bank Feeds.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Set Up the Envestnet Yodlee Bank Feeds Service](bank-how-setup-bank-statement-service.md).

seg-source.mrk: For more information, see [Set Up the Envestnet Yodlee Bank Feeds Service](bank-how-setup-bank-statement-service.md).

target.mrk: Pro více informací běžte na [Nastavení Envestnet yodlee Bank služby](bank-how-setup-bank-statement-service.md).

trans-unit.source: To import or export bank files, you must set up your own bank account and your vendors' bank accounts.

seg-source.mrk: To import or export bank files, you must set up your own bank account and your vendors' bank accounts.

target.mrk: Chcete-li importovat nebo exportovat bankovní soubory, musíte si nastavit vlastní bankovní účet a bankovní účty svých dodavatelů.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Set Up Bank Accounts](bank-how-setup-bank-accounts.md).

seg-source.mrk: For more information, see [Set Up Bank Accounts](bank-how-setup-bank-accounts.md).

target.mrk: Další informace naleznete v části [Nastavení bankovních účtů](bank-how-setup-bank-accounts.md).

trans-unit.source: The bank data conversion service may impose a limit on the number of lines that can be exported in one file.

seg-source.mrk: The bank data conversion service may impose a limit on the number of lines that can be exported in one file.

target.mrk: Služba převodu bankovních dat může omezit počet řádků, které lze exportovat do jednoho souboru.

trans-unit.source: You will receive an error message if the limit is exceeded.

seg-source.mrk: You will receive an error message if the limit is exceeded.

target.mrk: Při překročení limitu se zobrazí chybová zpráva.

trans-unit.source: It is recommended that bank statement files do not exceed 1000 lines as the processing time in the bank data conversion service may otherwise increase significantly.

seg-source.mrk: It is recommended that bank statement files do not exceed 1000 lines as the processing time in the bank data conversion service may otherwise increase significantly.

target.mrk: Doporučuje se, aby soubory bankovních výpisů nepřekročily 1000 řádků, jelikož doba zpracování v bankovní službě převodu dat se může výrazně zvýšit.

trans-unit.source: In the CRONUS International Ltd. demonstration database, the User Name and Password fields are prefilled with demonstration logon information, which you will replace with your company’s actual information as you sign up for the bank data conversion service.

trans-unit.source: In the **Sign-up URL** field, choose the browser button to open the service provider’s sign-up page.

trans-unit.source: On the sign-up page of the bank data service provider, enter the user name and password for your company’s subscription to the service, and then complete the sign-up process as instructed by the service provider.

trans-unit.source: Proceed to enter the user name and password that you specified for the service in the related setup fields in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: On the **Bank Data Conv. Service Setup** page, in the User **Name** field, enter the same value that you entered as logon name on the service provider’s page in step 4.

trans-unit.source: In the **Password** field, enter the same value that you entered in the **Password** field on the service provider’s page in step 4.
